{"tid":1433582,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗隻入]路西法效應：好人是如何變成惡魔的","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:46:11.000Z","uid":57911,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed38b20dd2da6b8e55eca211e3e123b46446e3a","tid":1433582,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"路西法效應是指在特定情境或氛圍下，思維方式、行為方式、人的性格，表現出了惡的一面，這體現了人性中的「惡」是可以人為在特定情境下，或是直接由情境造成的。<br />\n<br />\n1.首先，在有意或不經意之情形下跨越自己的道德底線。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">射頭、打頭、圍毆瞓低嘅示威者、亂棍扑途人</span><br />\n<br />\n2.將其他人或個體去人性化。<br />\n<br />\n3.將自己去識別化。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔出示委任證</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.分散與推諉個人之責任。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">將責任推落示威者嘅錯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.盲目服從於權威。<br />\n<br />\n6.不經批判地盲目服從團體規範。<br />\n<br />\n7.藉由不作為與冷漠，被動地容忍惡存在。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">不檢控白衫人或者遲遲唔拉人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/路西法效应\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E8%B7%AF%E8%A5%BF%E6%B3%95%E6%95%88%E5%BA%94&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9W58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=4e73ec3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/路西法效应</a>"},{"pid":"4bc7ecbc85cf0e993394982f9c15b327b5b1f8db","tid":1433582,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"歡迎狗隻入嚟討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b3018e3e7ea081cc876ca911c2b0b2b418a869","tid":1433582,"uid":2562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"［緊急］荃灣被斬義士⋯⋯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433055</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有冇文宣幫幫手<img